BindBC Library Licenses
=======================

The BindBC libraries used in this project are licensed under the Boost Software License.
These libraries provide bindings to the following native libraries:

Libraries:
- bindbc-glfw (GLFW bindings) - See LICENSE/GLFW
- bindbc-opengl (OpenGL bindings) - See LICENSE/OpenGL
- bindbc-openal (OpenAL bindings) - See LICENSE/OpenAL

See: https://github.com/BindBC for each library's license

